  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FormSection
    This class is responsible for presenting a form to the user and storing the answers.
    MenuSection
    This class is responsible for showing a menu to the user and activating the appropriate method.
    Section

    SelectionSection<Type>
    This class is responsible for letting the user choose between a number of optionNames.
    TextSection
    This class is responsible for showing a piece of text to the user.
    TitleSection
    This class is responsible for showing a title.
